INDONESIA: Sampoerna denies link to Transmarco takeover.Sampoerna denies link to Transmarco takeover.Indonesia's leading cigarette maker PT Handjaya Mandala Sampoerna said on Tuesday it had no link to a move by majority owner Putera Sampoerna to take over Transmarco Holdings of Singapore."It is a private investment of Putera Sampoerna and his son Jonathan and there is no connection with PT HM Sampoerna," Ekadharmajanto Kasih, chief financial officer of the firm, told Reuters.Miel Investment Corp, wholly-owned by Putera Sampoerna, said on Saturday it was making a conditional takeover offer for Transmarco Holdings, a trading and telecommunications company.-- Jakarta newsroom +6221 384-6364